sellerAgent.name: Shelly Salas Your Home Sold Guaranteed

data.description: Come and discover country living at its finest. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath 2,400 Sqft barndominium is nestled on 3.87 acres with a perimeter fence and electric gate opener. In addition, it sports a partial inground pool with a deck and concrete pad. As you enter the front door, you’ll be greeted with sealed concrete floors throughout as well as ceiling fans with remotes. The flat-screen TV as seen in the picture along with in-wall surround sound in the living room conveys with the sale. Then into the kitchen which has an island and fully custom countertops of wood and epoxy. Moving through the house you will see each entry has its own pocket door. The primary bedroom has its own bathroom, with a custom wood and epoxy double sink countertop and walk-in closet. The attic is fully insulated with spray foam and a partial wooden floor, this area also houses the a.c. unit which makes it efficient for routine maintenance.  Let your imagination run with endless possibilities to remodel the attic into that special room of your choice. The garage is a spacious 2 car with carport. The seller is in the process of relocating and is very motivated. Come see to fully appreciate.
